      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "<p><i>α</i>-Fenchone is a pleasant-smelling terpenoid isolated from oil of lavender. Propose a pathway for the formation of <i>α</i>-fenchone from geranyl diphosphate. A carbocation rearrangement is required.</p>\n<img class=\"scaled-down-30\" src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBbkFZIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--fb3f8f7442d5ad89fadf962b74a59e684a54a31e/OChem_27_EC_021.jpg\" alt=\"The structure of alpha-fenchone. It is a bicyclo[2.2.1] heptane with two methyls at C 3, one methyl at C 1, and a carbonyl at C 2,\">",
